 2012-11052012-09-20,  PS,  ,  ,  , 
ActFirearms Act
SubjectUnited States Preclearance Officers (Land Borders) Exemption Order
PrecisUNITED STATES PRECLEARANCE OFFICERS (LAND BORDERS) EXEMPTION ORDER in order to provide The United States Customs and Border Protection preclearance officers with the temporary authority to possess firearms, ammunition and defensive spray for the duration of the pilot. The Order will expire on December 31, 2015.
